#. <section class="sutta" id="sn21.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn21.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 21"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 21"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn21.11:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhikkhuvagga"
msgstr "1. Monks"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 11. Mahākappinasutta → kappino (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn21.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Mahākappinasutta"
msgstr "11. With Mahākappina"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn21.11:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahākappino yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami."
msgstr "Then Venerable Mahākappina went to see the Buddha."

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.3"
msgid "Addasā kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ mahākappinaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ."
msgstr "The Buddha saw him coming off in the distance,"

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.4"
msgid "Disvāna bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "and addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.5"
msgid ""
"“passatha no tumhe, bhikkhave, etaṃ bhikkhuṃ āgacchantaṃ odātakaṃ tanukaṃ "
"tuṅganāsikan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, do you you see that monk coming—white, thin, with a pointy "
"nose?”"

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.6"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.7"
msgid "“Eso kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu mahiddhiko mahānubhāvo."
msgstr ""
"“That mendicant is very mighty and powerful. It’s not easy to find an "
"attainment that he has not already attained."

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.8"
msgid "Na ca sā samāpatti sulabharūpā yā tena bhikkhunā asamāpannapubbā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.9"
msgid ""
"Yassa catthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti "
"tadanuttaraṃ brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā "
"sacchikatvā upasampajja viharatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"And he has realized the supreme end of the spiritual path in this very life. "
"He lives having achieved with his own insight the goal for which people from "
"good families rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn21.11:2.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "sn21.11:2.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā:"
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn21.11:3.1"
msgid "“Khattiyo seṭṭho janetasmiṃ,"
msgstr "“The aristocrat is best of those people"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:3.2"
msgid "ye gottapaṭisārino;"
msgstr "who take clan as the standard."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:3.3"
msgid "Vijjācaraṇasampanno,"
msgstr "But one accomplished in knowledge and conduct"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:3.4"
msgid "so seṭṭho devamānuse."
msgstr "is best of gods and humans."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.1"
msgid "Divā tapati ādicco,"
msgstr "The sun shines by day,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.2"
msgid "rattimābhāti candimā;"
msgstr "the moon glows at night,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.3"
msgid "Sannaddho khattiyo tapati,"
msgstr "the aristocrat shines in armor,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.4"
msgid "jhāyī tapati brāhmaṇo;"
msgstr "and the brahmin shines in absorption."

#. <br>
#. VAR: Atha sabbamahorattiṃ → atha sabbamahorattaṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.5"
msgid "Atha sabbamahorattiṃ,"
msgstr "But all day and all night,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.6"
msgid "buddho tapati tejasā”ti."
msgstr "the Buddha shines with glory.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.7"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
